    <h1>Making the Reddit Bot</h1>
<p>go to <a href="https://blog.syntonic.io/2017/07/07/reddit-bot-nodejs-example/" target="_blank"> for a step by step process</a> on how to install node js, snoowrap, snoostorm, dotenv and get your initial JS file set up. for the client ID and secret etc you must put it directly in the file not in a .env file because this is iffy on the raspberry pi</p>
<p>Next go to github abd retrieve the <a href="https://github.com/cdoern/takecareofourplants"target="_blank">index.js </a> file which has al of the code. you will have errors since you do not have the correct libraries installed, the file tells you what to install at the top.</p>
